151
00:09:05,810 --> 00:09:08,240
Oh, we came to hang out for a bit.

152
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:11,230
Yes, to hang out, for a bit.

153
00:09:11,230 --> 00:09:14,100
We also had some things to discuss.

154
00:09:20,530 --> 00:09:21,850
You guys, don't tell me...

155
00:09:21,850 --> 00:09:24,460
President! I mean, Ajussi.

156
00:09:24,460 --> 00:09:26,410
