157
00:09:26,410 --> 00:09:28,750
He's been staying at our house for a short while.

158
00:09:29,530 --> 00:09:33,230
He's called Drill, he is my friend and also a trainee.

159
00:09:33,230 --> 00:09:34,140
Greet him, Drill.

160
00:09:34,140 --> 00:09:36,470
Why do you...

161
00:09:38,330 --> 00:09:39,660
Good eve- ning.

162
00:09:39,660 --> 00:09:44,020
Ah, Mister, for me— Uuh, that is...

163
00:09:44,020 --> 00:09:47,260
Woo Seung also, she didn't have a place to go anymore.

164
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:51,880
I'm sorry, Father. I didn't do this to deceive you all this time.

165
00:09:53,140 --> 00:09:56,840
I'll keep on training. Please let me do this.

166
00:09:57,740 --> 00:09:59,760
- I'm sorry.
- We are sorry.

167
00:09:59,760 --> 00:10:02,000
Let's talk again tomorrow.

168
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:06,060
