177
00:10:25,950 --> 00:10:28,930
What's more, it's as a singer. You could even help him out.

178
00:10:28,930 --> 00:10:33,300
Why do you keep on telling him to be a civil servant when he doesn't want to? Is it because of money?

179
00:10:33,300 --> 00:10:35,810
Hey. Get a grip.

180
00:10:35,810 --> 00:10:40,190
Even if you say you don't remember, Ji Hoon is your son.

181
00:10:41,920 --> 00:10:44,890
