182
00:10:44,890 --> 00:10:46,970
Yeah. Why can't he?

183
00:10:47,010 --> 00:10:50,060
Right, you spoke well. He is my child, in fact.

184
00:10:50,060 --> 00:10:52,880
Because he's my child, you can't beat his instinct with rationality.

185
00:10:52,880 --> 00:10:57,090
Don't you see? You've been pressing it down firmly, but it bursts out every time.

186
00:10:57,110 --> 00:11:02,300
His talent, that is condensed somewhere deep inside his heart, he himself can't reject it.

187
00:11:02,300 --> 00:11:05,650
Anyway. Ahh, he really is mine.

188
00:11:06,130 --> 00:11:08,460
Little punk.

189
00:11:09,270 --> 00:11:10,970
- Damn it!
- Hey.

190
00:11:10,970 --> 00:11:13,520
Don't say whatever you want. Ji Hoon is my child!

191
00:11:13,520 --> 00:11:16,320
You're the one who said he is mine!

192
00:11:16,320 --> 00:11:19,970
That we live like this now, does it look good to you?

193
00:11:19,970 --> 00:11:21,700
No, I mean.

194
00:11:21,700 --> 00:11:24,500
Bo Hee can't even tell her son that he is hers.

195
00:11:24,510 --> 00:11:27,680
And me, in my own way... And Ji Hoon, this guy, too!

196
00:11:28,390 --> 00:11:30,390
Forget it. Shut up.

197
00:11:30,390 --> 00:11:34,420
No, but you can't tell Ji Hoon that he is Bo Hee's son?

198
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:36,350
- Why?
- Shut up,

199
00:11:36,410 --> 00:11:39,680
and leave this house. It has become too dangerous. That won't do.

200
00:11:39,680 --> 00:11:41,380
- No.
- Why?

201
00:11:41,460 --> 00:11:47,010
