206
00:12:01,710 --> 00:12:07,340
The first payment from our album, that I left before coming over. It's somewhere here, for sure.

207
00:12:07,940 --> 00:12:11,230
Hey. It's no less than two billion won. Two billion!

208
00:12:11,270 --> 00:12:13,990
Let's find it together, uh?

209
00:12:15,030 --> 00:12:17,620
What the hell are you talking about?

210
00:12:17,620 --> 00:12:21,720
