216
00:12:37,820 --> 00:12:42,850
You'd forget him and let him go after his memorial service. Did you or didn't you?

217
00:12:43,470 --> 00:12:48,140
From now on, don't ever mention Hyeon Jae's name with your mouth again.

218
00:12:48,140 --> 00:12:50,870
