225
00:13:07,100 --> 00:13:10,970
No. It's okay. It's already late.

226
00:13:10,970 --> 00:13:15,210
What a fool. We threw you a party to feed you a good meal and you couldn't even eat it and just left.

227
00:13:15,250 --> 00:13:19,140
What the hell did you pick up from the floor earlier that made you jump up and run so suddenly?

228
00:13:19,140 --> 00:13:21,750
I said it was nothing. You should rest.

229
00:13:21,750 --> 00:13:23,650
- Go to sleep immediately.
- Okay.

230
00:13:23,650 --> 00:13:24,430
Let's go in.

231
00:13:24,430 --> 00:13:27,570
Aigoo. What a pathetic guy. My legs hurt.

232
00:13:27,570 --> 00:13:29,370
