240
00:14:34,560 --> 00:14:38,020
I heard that before I was born he abandoned me and my mom.

241
00:14:38,900 --> 00:14:41,710
He just left us and went somewhere.

242
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:46,790
Was he originally a selfish person who only cares for himself?

243
00:14:50,400 --> 00:14:53,590
This is the first time that I've ever wanted to do something.

244
00:14:54,630 --> 00:14:58,350
Yet, it's the first time I can't do it. No matter how much effort I put in it.

245
00:14:59,790 --> 00:15:04,520
