- Tell us!
- Be honest about what?

503
00:30:32,050 --> 00:30:36,970
How dare you? I've lived my whole life making a living by studying people with just an eye.

504
00:30:36,990 --> 00:30:40,860
I don't know if you can fool anyone else, but you can't fool me.

505
00:30:40,860 --> 00:30:43,180
You can't fool me.

506
00:30:44,110 --> 00:30:47,800
Mal Sook. When adults are talking, why do you keep interfering?

507
00:30:47,800 --> 00:30:50,060
Be quiet, you are distracting me.

508
00:30:50,060 --> 00:30:54,510
You... Tell us the truth! I already know everything, you punk.

509
00:30:54,510 --> 00:30:57,670
I'm really not him. Hey, Soondae...

510
00:30:58,780 --> 00:31:02,960
What? You just called me "Soondae"?

511
00:31:02,960 --> 00:31:09,780
You see. I was right! You, Hyeon Jae, always used to call me President Soondae, you punk!

512
00:31:09,780 --> 00:31:13,490
You! You have been caught red-handed by me!

513
00:31:13,490 --> 00:31:15,940
Look at you.

514
00:31:15,940 --> 00:31:18,180
- We are back!
- We are back!

515
00:31:19,080 --> 00:31:21,880
We are back home!

516
00:31:25,320 --> 00:31:27,660
Hey! Why are you down here?

517
00:31:27,660 --> 00:31:29,550
Well, I was told to eat some bread.

518
00:31:29,550 --> 00:31:33,600
Gwang Jae. This punk is really Hyeon Jae.

519
00:31:33,600 --> 00:31:36,010
No. President, what's wrong with you again?

520
00:31:36,010 --> 00:31:39,300
This punk just called me Soondae.

521
00:31:39,300 --> 00:31:43,020
"President Soondae." Only Hyeon Jae used to call me that back then.

522
00:31:43,020 --> 00:31:44,090
What?

523
00:31:44,090 --> 00:31:47,530
This punk called me Soondae. Soondae. Soondae.

524
00:31:47,530 --> 00:31:50,120
- Oh, I'm sure you heard wrong.
- Again I heard wrong?

525
00:31:50,160 --> 00:31:54,420
Excuse me. Can you look after the store for a while? Bo Hee and I have to go out for a meeting.

526
00:31:54,420 --> 00:31:58,060
- What kind of meeting?
- Bo Hee got an offer for a commercial.

527
00:31:58,100 --> 00:32:01,280
Really? Good job. You did well.

528
00:32:04,180 --> 00:32:07,130
Come here, let's go.

529
00:32:11,950 --> 00:32:14,410
The Best Hit
